<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Peer Evaluation</title>
    <style>
        .container {
            width: 50%;
            margin: 0 auto;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .title {
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        table {
            width: 100%;
        }
        th, td {
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: left;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="title">
            <h2>Peer Evaluation</h2>
        </div>
        <p>Questions to consider when evaluating your peers:</p>
        <ul style="text-align: left;">
            <li>Did they do their fair share of the work?</li>
            <li>Did they complete assigned tasks?</li>
            <li>Were they actively engaged in discussions?</li>
            <li>Did they seem motivated to work?</li>
            <li>Were they prompt in their communication?</li>
            <li>Did they meet deadlines?</li>
            <li>Was the quality of their work acceptable?</li>
            <li>Did they have a positive and helpful attitude?</li>
            <li>Were they willing to accept more responsibility?</li>
            <li>Would you like to work with this person again?</li>
        </ul>
        <form method="post" action="/submit">
            <table>
                <tr>
                    <th>Student Name</th>
                    <th>Rating (0-100)</th>
                    <th>Comments</th>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Student 1</td>
                    <td><input type="range" min="0" max="100" value="50" step="1"></td>
                    <td><textarea rows="3" cols="30"></textarea></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Student 2</td>
                    <td><input type="range" min="0" max="100" value="50" step="1"></td>
                    <td><textarea rows="3" cols="30"></textarea></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Student 3</td>
                    <td><input type="range" min="0" max="100" value="50" step="1"></td>
                    <td><textarea rows="3" cols="30"></textarea></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Student 4</td>
                    <td><input type="range" min="0" max="100" value="50" step="1"></td>
                    <td><textarea rows="3" cols="30"></textarea></td>
                </tr>
            </table>
            <br>
            <input type="submit" value="Submit">
        </form>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
